## code
Take the 10th value of `x` and assign it to a new variable.  
  * Name this new variable `y`.
```r
x <- c(
  7, 10, 8, 6, 7, 10, 8, 8,
  8, 9, 7, 9, 6, 7, 5, 7,
  10, 6, 9, 9, 9, 8, 8, 10,
  10, 6, 9, 6, 8, 8, 6, 9
)
y <- x[10]
```
